WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.242 --> 00:00:04.039
When I was very young

00:00:06.643 --> 00:00:08.862
I was taken away from my Mom.

00:00:11.642 --> 00:00:13.909
I was forced to live...

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:18.552
In a filthy, crowded place.

00:00:21.177 --> 00:00:23.403
It was very sad.

00:00:26.257 --> 00:00:28.770
I was very LONELY.

00:00:31.349 --> 00:00:33.969
I missed my Mom.

00:00:36.623 --> 00:00:39.334
I barely had any room...

00:00:41.791 --> 00:00:43.998
To move around.

00:00:47.095 --> 00:00:49.277
Time went by.

00:00:51.272 --> 00:00:53.503
Then...

00:00:56.109 --> 00:00:58.441
I became pregnant.

00:01:01.681 --> 00:01:04.040
I didn't want to.

00:01:07.204 --> 00:01:09.540
For 9 months...

00:01:12.092 --> 00:01:14.587
I felt my baby grow.

00:01:17.228 --> 00:01:19.853
When she was born...

00:01:22.789 --> 00:01:25.599
I fell in love!

00:01:28.502 --> 00:01:31.600
She was so beautiful.

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:37.400
But...

00:01:39.777 --> 00:01:42.939
I only had ONE day with her.

00:01:45.707 --> 00:01:48.303
Then...
the men came.

00:01:51.015 --> 00:01:53.608
And took her away.

00:01:56.562 --> 00:01:58.923
I tried to fight.

00:02:01.848 --> 00:02:04.452
I cried.

00:02:07.052 --> 00:02:10.046
But she was gone.

00:02:13.037 --> 00:02:15.494
I was hooked up...

00:02:18.233 --> 00:02:20.377
To machines.

00:02:22.793 --> 00:02:25.318
That took my milk.

00:02:27.924 --> 00:02:30.565
The milk I made...

00:02:33.096 --> 00:02:35.731
For my baby girl.

00:02:38.649 --> 00:02:40.603
This is me...

00:02:49.053 --> 00:02:51.665
I'm speaking for her.

00:02:54.335 --> 00:02:57.362
Because she can't.

00:03:00.184 --> 00:03:02.775
Please don't consume

00:03:05.121 --> 00:03:07.732
DAIRY.

00:03:09.704 --> 00:03:11.989
See for yourself...

